TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me want some informations.
Goodbye.
Me want to know about different city areas.
Text: 나 도시 다른 구역들 알고 싶어.

TextEng: What do you know of the plague?
I need infomation about places in Neverwinter.
Text: 네버윈터의 여러 장소들에 대한 정보가 필요해.

TextEng: Have you heard of anything odd? Any rumors?
Text: 이상한 일 들어본 적 있어? 소문이든 뭐든?

TextEng: You know anything about the bad plague?
Text: 나쁜 역병, 뭐 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Me wants information about places in Neverwinter.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
What do you know about attempts at a cure?
Text: 치료제를 만드는 시도에 대해 뭘 알아?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Do you mean physically or spiritually?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 육체적으로 말하는 건가, 영적으로 말하는 건가?

TextEng: I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
What are the different areas of the city?
Beggar's Nest.
Docks district.
Blacklake district.
Peninsula.
Where can I get equipment?
Where me get equipment?
City Core.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> What do you know about that?
You can tell me. We are <race> kin.
We both <race> kind. Why not tell me?
Text: 우리 둘 다 <race>야. 왜 말 안 해?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You know anything abouts that?
I need to ask about the other districts.
Me ask about other city areas.
Woulds you buy cure for bad plague if someone offer?
Text: 누가 안 좋은 역병 치료제 팔면 살 거야?

TextEng: Would you buy a cure if it was offered?
Nevermind. Me just ask other questions.
Text: 아니야. 나 그냥 다른 것 물어볼게.

TextEng: Nevermind. I just have a few other questions.
Text: 아니, 됐어. 다른 질문 몇 개만 할게.

TextEng: Me ask to see if you gots gold! Give it, now!
Text: 나 금 있는지 보려고 물어본 거야! 이제 내놔!

TextEng: To find out if you have gold! Hand it over, now!
Text: 네가 돈 있는지 알아내려고! 이제 내놔!

TextEng: Me just teasing yous. Me sorry. Really.
Text: 나 그냥 장난친 거야. 나 미안해. 진짜.

TextEng: Ahh, I was just joking around. Sorry about that.
Me a guard and you is nobody! You give gold or you die like dog!
Text: 나 경비고 너는 아무것도 아냐! 너 금 주든지 개처럼 죽든지!

TextEng: I'm a guard and you are nobody. Hand over your gold or die like a dog!
Text: 난 경비고 넌 아무것도 아니야. 금 내놔, 안 그럼 개처럼 죽어!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Me gots the cure! You give all yous gold and you get it!
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 나 치료제 있어! 너 금 다 주면 줄게!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> I have the cure! Give me all your gold and you can have it!
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 내게 치료제가 있어! 금 다 내놓으면 줄게!

TextEng: Me just ask to see if you gots gold! Give it, now!
Text: 나 그냥 너 금 있나 보려고 물어본 거야! 이제 내놔!

TextEng: Bah! I just asked to see if you had gold! Give it to me!
Text: 쳇! 그냥 돈 있나 확인한 거야! 이제 내놔!

TextEng: Me gots to make a living. Just business, okay?
Text: 나 돈 벌어야 해. 그냥 장사야, 알겠어?

TextEng: Don't take it too hard. It's just business.
Text: 너무 심각하게 받아들이지 마. 그냥 장사일 뿐이야.

TextEng: Yous really stupid! HAW!
HAHAHA! What an idiot!
